value.name: A League of Their Own Road Trip: Loch Ness to London
value.original_name: A League of Their Own Road Trip: Loch Ness to London
value.overview: The boys hit the road once more as Jamie Redknapp, Freddie Flintoff and Romesh Ranganathan are joined by a certain Jack Whitehall, as they travel from Loch Ness in Scotland to London.
